Test improvments
* Make tests faster
  - precompile so we don't need to wait so long at startup of each test
  - faster timeouts, move flaky tests to "slow" set
* more helper funcs (e.g. almostExplode)
  - make tests use them (e.g. "max games" does not)
* better locators (e.g. cards in a modal derives from the modal not the page)
* remove unused locator consts
* Add a prod test with cases which do not need DEVMODE
   - e.g. prove the animation
* Add more stability and hand-wrap tests for different screen dimensions
* A worker process has failed to exit gracefully and has been force exited. This is likely caused by tests leaking due to improper teardown. Try running with --detectOpenHandles to find leaks. Active timers can also cause this, ensure that .unref() was called on them.
* simplify context + page -> browser.newPage

